# SHACL SHAPES — key axiom constraints
# (Requires sh: prefix; import separately if needed)
# ============================================================

# Shape for Axiom 7: correlativity within ODRLRelator
# Shape for Axiom 9: disability precludes prohibition creation
# Shape for Unique Founding (Axiom 5)
